title: Star Wars Episode II: Attack of The Phantom
description:
Episode II re-cut by the Phantom Editor.  Mike J cut 38 minutes out of AOTC to create this version. An excellent follow up to The Phantom Edit.

Here's a link to a TFN review: http://www.theforce.net/rouser/reviews/phantom_attack.asp

Ripped from DVD image.

Download that image here:
Play that image with VLC:
www.videolan.org

Again, this torrent is just the movie.  Thefile is for the DVD image, which you can either burn and watch on your player, or just play off your computer with VLC.  It's much bigger, but it's worth it for the commentary track.

Thanks Mike J!

Now, if we could only get Revenge of the Phantom...
